							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I finally got mine working.
<br />

<br />
Mistakes I was making:
<br />

<br />
/g instead of  ; gsay
<br />

<br />
/doability instead of /useability
<br />

<br />
and having too many / floating throughout
<br />

<br />
I don't remember the exact thing I figured out.. but I did get it after awhile. Especially once I figured out the "gsay" thing.  
<br />

<br />
Good luck!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
